&lt;li&gt;Work closely with our development and AI teams to deliver solutions that increase efficiency and stability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;Qualifications&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Must-have:&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;BS or MS in software engineering, computer science, or a related field.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven experience standing up a CI/CD system from scratch.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with multi-language build systems (e.g., Bazel, Bob).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency with cloud platforms (e.g., AWS, Azure, GCP) and containerization technologies (e.g., Docker, Kubernetes).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with automation tools (e.g., Terraform, Ansible, GitHub Actions, Jenkins) and version control systems (e.g., Git).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong programming skills in languages such as Python, Go, or Java.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Self-starter attitude with strong ability to identify problems, prioritize them, then plan and execute working solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enthusiasm for working in a fast paced startup environment and eagerness to support the team on a variety of topics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Nice-to-have:&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
