&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of big data technologies (e.g., Hadoop, Spark, or Kafka).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with monitoring and observability tools (e.g., Prometheus, Grafana, ELK stack).&lt;/li&gt;
