&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;h1&gt;Role Description&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking an exceptional Sr. Mechanical Engineer to design and test innovative robotic hardware ranging from overall robot architecture down to detailed design of robot subassemblies and mechanisms.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this role you will:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Brainstorm and develop innovative and practical concepts for general purpose robotic systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with our business development, modeling &amp;amp; simulation, software, integration &amp;amp; testing, and industrial design teams to define loading conditions, performance requirements and packaging.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design assemblies and components in 3D CAD from conceptual architecture through detailed design and drawing release.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with vendors and manufacturers to produce your components.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support assembly, integration, and testing of robotic hardware.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;Qualifications&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Must-have:&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5+ years of experience in mechanical engineering.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s or Master’s Degree in mechanical engineering, robotics, mechatronics, or similar field.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Expert user of 3D CAD software to design complex parts and assemblies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with structural design and analysis principles including FEA.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with electromechanical integration, including motors, sensors, servo drives, speed reducers, electronics packaging, and wiring.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Self-starter attitude with strong ability to identify problems, prioritize them, then plan and execute working solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enthusiasm for working in a fast paced startup environment and eagerness to support the team on a variety of topics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Nice-to-have:&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience designing high performance robotic systems including actuators and dexterous end-effectors.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience designing and analyzing structures that are highly optimized for mass and stiffness.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High volume manufacturing experience.&amp;nbsp; Design of cast and molded parts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
